Package: tidywigits
Title: Tidy WiGiTS
Version: 0.0.4.9001
Description: Tidies outputs from The Hartwig Medical Foundation's WiGiTS
             suite of genome and transcriptome analysis tools.
             Writes to various formats for downstream ingestion
             into data warehouses and databases.
